[font=Trebuchet MS][img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_Description.png[/img]

[font=Arial]Millepon Diamond ENB is custom remodeling ENB of based on mix of RealLike ENB and RealVision ENB.
This ENB is customize in reality emphasis not disturb the color of vanilla as possible.
For example reflection of sky and sun shine, [font=Trebuchet MS][font=Arial]light [/font][/font]and shadow setting etc...
and this ENB is suitable for High Resolution texture MOD because graphic quality is very sharp by FXAA setting.
Also created aimed at lightness that does not feel stress in gaming.

The following is a Quality Version

PC environment (GTX760, Core i7 2600, MEM8GB, FullHD) in the outdoor average 40 ~ 55FPS, in the indoor has come out 55[font=Trebuchet MS][font=Arial] ~ [/font][/font]60FPS.
[font=Trebuchet MS][font=Arial]PC environment (GTX970, Core i7 2600, MEM8GB, FullHD) in the outdoor
average 45 ~ 60FPS, in the indoor has come out always 60FPS.[/font][/font]
PC environment (GTX980, Core i7 2600, MEM8GB, FullHD) in the outdoor
average 50 ~ 60FPS, in the indoor has come out always 60FPS.

Above optimize performance in the [size=5][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58100/]Skyrim INI Manager[/url] [/size]
Please refer to the distribution page for optimization.[/font][/font]


[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/Sample1.jpg[/img]

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_Tool.png[/img]

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_Config.jpg[/img]

You can easy setting by configuration tool "Diamond ENB Configurator" from version 1.3 or higher.
It is also possible to introduce leave the default setting, but it is recommended that you change from once tool.
Preferences before introducing the video memory to the appropriate setting.

Also by default setting has become a Quality version.
If you need Light version please change from the tool.

You can add an afterimage visual effects To further enable the EnableLongExposureMode so long ENB v0.272 more.
Please adjust by liking the Time and BlendMax value and the reflection time is an effective amount of afterimage.


[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/Sample6.jpg[/img]

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_Installation.png[/img]

1.Please download the [size=4][url=http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.htm]ENB v0.262 - v0.308[/url][/size]
2.Copy the d3d9.dll and enbhost.exe and this preset files in to the Skyrim folder.
(If you installed the other ENB, Remove all files and folders associated with previously installed ENB presets)

3.Edit your skyrimprefs.ini and set the following values.

[Display]
bFloatPointRenderTarget=1
bDrawLandShadows=1
bTreesReceiveShadows=1
bShadowsOnGrass=1
iMultiSample=0
bFXAAEnabled=0
iMaxAnisotropy=0
fGamma=1.0000

[Imagespace]
bDoDepthOfField=1


or Use my created tool [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58100/][size=4]Skyrim INI Manager[/size][/url]
you can easily set it!

1.click Display Settings tab
Set enable to ENB and Depth of Field setting.

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/INI1.jpg[/img]

2.Click Graphic Detail [1] tab of Performance tab.
And check the Land and Tree and Grass of Self Shadow setting.

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/INI2.jpg[/img]

3. Click Filemenu and SaveSettings.


[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/Sample5.jpg[/img]

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_Required.png[/img]

[size=5][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17802]Climates Of Tamriel - Weather - Lighting - Audio[/url][/size]
(Other weather MOD is not supported)

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_Recommended.png[/img]

[color=#ffff00][size=4][b]Highly Recommended!![/b][/size][/color]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64856/?]Skyrim HD - Terrain Parallax Tribute[/url] or [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/607]Skyrim HD - 2K Textures[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13268]WATER - Water And Terrain Enhancement Redux[/url]
[url=http://enbseries.enbdev.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=1499]Skyrim particle patch for ENB

[/url]
[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/Sample4.jpg[/img]

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_LUT.png[/img]

You can change to a fantasic or dramatic world with LUT filters.
There are registered 35 LUTs.
and you can register maximum 10 Custom LUTs.

[url=https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/62406-0-1503680974.jpg]Sample1[/url]  [url=https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/62406-1-1503680974.jpg]Sample2[/url]  [url=https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/62406-2-1503680973.jpg]Sample3[/url]

1. In the game, open the ENB setting screen with "Shift + Enter" and click "ENBEFFECT.FX" from the "Shader parameters" window.
2. Click the list of "TECHNIQUE" and select your favorite LUT.
3. Close the ENB selection screen with "Shift + Enter".

Custom 1 - Custom 10 are your self-made LUTs. (Custom 1 is a sample LUT with little brightness)
Please overwrite your own LUT to Custom_LUT1.bmp ~ Custom_LUT10.bmp.

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/SampleLUT.jpg[/img]

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_Uninstall.png[/img]

Please delete d3d9.dll and enbhost.exe and this preset files in Skyrim folder.
Recommend use the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7804]ENB FXAA SweetFX Manager and Remover[/url]

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/Sample7.jpg[/img]

[img]http://tepodon.blog.jp/Nexus/Diamond_ENB/ENB_Credits.png[/img]

Q. When installing on Windows10, I get an error saying "createdxgifactory2 d3d11.dll was not found" at startup.

A. In Windows10, dxgi.dll of SweetFX conflicts with the graphic driver,
please copy dxgi.dll from the Windows\System32 folder to the Skyrim folder.

Q.Why my captured Screenshots is pale in color?

A.This ENB using the SweetFX and adjusted it.
So, only ENB capture function is different visual.
Please use the "Fraps" or other capture tool.

Q.I'm using this ENB, but It is not same color as screenshots.

A.Did you use the other ENB before this ENB?
If you used other ENB, probably another files is remaining.
Please data folder to clean state, before introducing the ENB.
High Recommended use the "[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7804]ENB FXAA SweetFX Manager and Remover[/url]"

Q.Black skin character become jet black, how to fix?

A.This ENB has high contrast color of the entire.
So, color close to black is looks like darker.
You can use the Facelight or temporarily press ScrollLock key for turn off the SweetFX.
